Package: ORSRouting
Type: Package
Title: Bulk routing distance computations using OpenRouteService
Version: 0.8.0
Date: 2022-02-14
Authors@R: person("Lieth", "Jonas", email = "jonas.lieth@gesis.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jonas Lieth <jonas.lieth@gesis.org>
Description: Interface to custom OpenRouteService setups that allows computing
    the (shortest) routing distances of entire georeferenced datasets to certain
    points of interest and inspecting specific routes in greater detail. To
    process larger datasets and allow for unrestricted API requests, the
    package functions rely on a local Docker setup of the OpenRouteService
    backend that can be set up and controlled using an integrated R6 class.
Encoding: UTF-8
